    <item>
      <title>如果欧盟解冻资金，匈牙利愿意取消乌克兰援助否决权</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-12/hungary-says-it-may-lift-ukraine-aid-veto-if-eu-unfreezes-funds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[匈牙利总理欧尔班·维克多的首席政治顾问表示，匈牙利准备取消对欧盟向乌克兰提供大规模资助提案的否决权，以换取欧盟因民主倒退而扣留布达佩斯的数十亿美元资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-12/hungary-says-it-may-lift-ukraine-aid-veto-if-eu-unfreezes-funds</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Dec 2023 17:44:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
